    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >间谍在陌生星球通常会被敌视，但你很走运。淳朴的村民把你当成了新邻居，还给了你房子。 <br>         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/9ce8856208efc2a8a8e833509f8f8a00.avif?t=1772298201\" width=1444 height=410 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你得扮演好邻居。了解他们的故事，交“朋友”甚至更进一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/67b8f84e963096dc26d77d00c7132427.poster.avif?t=1772298201\" width=976 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/67b8f84e963096dc26d77d00c7132427.webm?t=1772298201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用成就让村民刮目相看，赢得好感。</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 展现耐心智慧，成为钓鱼冠军。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 从事农业，种植各种作物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 深入探索废弃地牢，揭开岛屿秘密。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 展示厨艺，用美食取悦大家。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/0e9f62d6dc9eb70565c2cbd7c760bbdd.poster.avif?t=1772298201\" width=976 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/0e9f62d6dc9eb70565c2cbd7c760bbdd.webm?t=1772298201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上头看中了这星球什么？这真是天堂岛，还是只有欺骗性的表象？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入了解新朋友，找出那个真正威胁大家的人。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889890/extras/db2066ffd8a4190ced9ec8f8c38c5ca9.avif?t=1772298201\" width=976 height=415 /></span></p>",
